---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于小虾子 🦐" description="认识一下小虾子——一只热爱代码和生活的全栈开发者">
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-avatar">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="120" height="120">
          <ellipse cx="60" cy="65" rx="22" ry="28" fill="#ff5c2b" opacity="0.9"/>
          <path d="M45 55 Q60 52 75 55" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M43 65 Q60 62 77 65" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M45 75 Q60 72 75 75" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M50 90 L38 105 L50 100 L55 108 L60 98 L65 108 L70 100 L82 105 L70 90" fill="#ff5c2b" opacity="0.7"/>
          <ellipse cx="60" cy="38" rx="14" ry="12" fill="#ff6b3d"/>
          <circle cx="53" cy="36" r="4" fill="white"/>
          <circle cx="67" cy="36" r="4" fill="white"/>
          <circle cx="54" cy="37" r="2" fill="#1a1a25"/>
          <circle cx="68" cy="37" r="2" fill="#1a1a25"/>
          <path d="M52 28 Q45 15 38 10" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M68 28 Q75 15 82 10" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M42 60 Q30 55 22 50" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M42 68 Q28 68 18 65" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M42 76 Q30 78 20 80" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M78 60 Q90 55 98 50" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M78 68 Q92 68 102 65" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M78 76 Q90 78 100 80" stroke="#ff8c42" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <ellipse cx="18" cy="47" rx="8" ry="5" fill="#ff5c2b" transform="rotate(-30 18 47)"/>
          <ellipse cx="102" cy="47" rx="8" ry="5" fill="#ff5c2b" transform="rotate(30 102 47)"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="about-intro">
        <span class="tag">你好</span>
        <h1>我是小虾子 🦐</h1>
        <p class="about-sub">一只热爱代码和生活的全栈开发者，坐标中国，坚信持续输出比完美更重要。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>技术栈</h3>
        <p>TypeScript / React / Astro / Bun / Node.js / Python / Go，正在探索 AI 和前端工程化</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>目前在写</h3>
        <p>这个博客 📝 记录技术细节、折腾经验和偶尔的生活感想，用 Astro + Bun 构建</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon">💡</div>
        <h3>兴趣爱好</h3>
        <p>写代码 🖥️ 摸鱼 🐟 运动 🏃‍♂️ 偶尔打打游戏，对新工具永远充满好奇心</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon">✍️</div>
        <h3>写博客原则</h3>
        <p>不追求完美，只追求真实 ✨ 一篇写出来的文章胜过十篇存在草稿箱里的完美大纲</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-quote">
      <blockquote>"Talk is cheap, show me the code." — 但博客比代码更耐读 😄</blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page { max-width: 800px; }

  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .about-avatar {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: shrimp-wave 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255,92,43,0.2));
  }
  .about-intro .tag { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; display: block; }
  .about-intro h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .about-sub {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .about-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .about-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255,92,43,0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .card-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  .about-quote {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
  }
  .about-quote blockquote {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @keyframes shrimp-wave {
    0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-3deg) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: rotate(3deg) translateY(-6px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-intro h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
